    <text id="B0529T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>How asks for three officers to be stationed at several places in the
                    Sub-District.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">R.F. &amp;
                        A.L.</abbr><lb/><abbr expan="Headquarters">Hd Qrs</abbr> 6th <abbr
                            expan="District">Dist</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr>
                    <name type="recipient"><abbr expan="Colonel">Col.</abbr> O. Brown<lb/><abbr
                            expan="Assistant Commissioner">Asst. Comr.</abbr> Richmond, <abbr
                            expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1865-08-15"><abbr expan="August">Augt</abbr> 15th 1865</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Colonel</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have the honor to request the assignment of three (3) officers for duty in this
                    District in the Counties of Botetourt (Sub<abbr expan="District">Dist</abbr>
                    "A"), Alleghany, Bath (Sub <abbr expan="District">Dist</abbr> "B") and
                    Rockbridge (Sub <abbr expan="District">Dist</abbr> "C")</p>

                <p>On application to <abbr expan="Lieutenant Colonel">Lt. Col.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="Cecil">C.</abbr> Clay 58th <abbr expan="Pennsylvania Volunteers"
                        >Pa. Vols.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="commanding">comd'g</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="Sub-District">Sub. Dist.</abbr> of Staunton he answers "I have no
                    officers I can let you have as assistants -- I have seven (7) companies with but
                    four (4) officers one of whom is acting adjutant leaving three (3) officers for
                    duty with seven (7) Companies."</p>

                <p>The officers desired are necessary for the proper and immediate organization of
                    the District.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am Colonel<lb/>Very Respectfully<lb/>Your <abbr
                            expan="Obedient Servant">Obt Servt</abbr></salute>
                    <signed>W. Storer How<lb/><abbr expan="Captain and Assistant Quartermaster">Capt
                            &amp; AQM</abbr><lb/><abbr expan="Superintendent">Supt.</abbr> Sixth
                            <abbr expan="District">Dist</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
